{"tid":1794024,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"英國女童購中國製聖誕卡發現卡上寫上求救訊息 聲稱上海青浦監獄是血汗工場","createTime":"2019-12-22T22:32:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T04:22:55.000Z","uid":266325,"like":78,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"1afa33e0707d7febe8dece821a4ef11cc15c2bc7","tid":1794024,"uid":266325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T22:32:22.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】英國一名女童購買中國製的慈善聖誕卡後，發現有人在其中一張卡上寫上求救訊息，聲稱上海青浦監獄是血汗工場。 <br />\n<br />\n發現訊息的六歲女童是來自倫敦南部的維迪科姆，她早前在當地超市Tesco買了一盒聖誕卡後，發現其中一張已被人用過，並在卡上用英語寫下訊息，聲稱自己是上海青浦監獄的外國囚犯，又說他們被迫勞動，希望收到訊息的人幫助他們通知人權組織，和聯繫曾經同樣被囚禁在青浦監獄的英國前記者、前企業欺詐調查員漢弗萊。<br />\n<br />\nTesco發言人回應時說，對有關消息感到震驚，聲言公司討厭使用監獄勞工，宣布立即停止跟相關中國工廠合作並展開調查，超市亦會停售有關聖誕卡。<br />\n<br />\n上海都係春袋呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62b40976b64bad3e006cd5113cd15c2ef64e645e","tid":1794024,"uid":248098,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T22:39:04.000Z","msg":"2020 上海取代香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e0198f66a4c785dc3bb21f11cb2f5b3fb7f3f68","tid":1794024,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T22:47:39.000Z","msg":"那邊襄Uniqle 無良印品 H&amp;M 繼續賣新疆集中營製綿<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />港豬繼續幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feda00e1341e91dda324ef80b936db8013fc7b3a","tid":1794024,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62b40976b64bad3e006cd5113cd15c2ef64e645e","tid":1794024,"uid":248098,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T22:39:04.000Z","msg":"2020 上海取代香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T22:48:03.000Z","msg":"算唔算導彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8a64ff1bb32930b49eb2